## Known Characteristics of Iris Species:
- 'Setosa':
  - Typically has the shortest petal length (1-2 cm) and the widest petal width (0.5-1 cm).
  - Typically has the shortest sepal length (2-3 cm) and the widest sepal width (1-2 cm).
- 'Versicolor':
  - Typically has petal lengths between 4-8 cm and petal widths between 1-2 cm.
